biography: Your tour guide for the beautiful city of Redmond, WA. Whether you're a local or just visiting, we invite you to Geek Out in Redmond!

latestIgtvVideos.title: “You Stay, We Pay”
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Special thank you to @kiro7seattle for their excellent coverage of our "You Stay, We Pay" program. 🛌💸 Visit GeekOutInRedmond.com to learn more & book your stay! OurRedmond #GeekOutInRedmond

latestIgtvVideos.title: Dusting for Fingerprints!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Dusting for fingerprints with chocolate… Yes. 👀 You read that right. 🚓 Sgt. Julie Beard shows us how to get creative at home! 🙃 Check out @redmondwapolice — their page will keep us all virtually engaged! 😊

latestPosts.caption: Redmond Derby Days is back this Friday & Saturday at Redmond City Hall Campus! 🎉 Don’t miss live music on the Microsoft Main Stage, a dazzling drone show Saturday night at 10:10 p.m., and so much more. 🎶✨

Big scoops are coming to Redmond! 🎉🍦

Join us Saturday, July 5th, for the grand opening of Salt & Straw’s newest shop. Swing by early for a free drink from Boon Boona Coffee and indulge in classic and limited-time flavors all day long (11AM–11PM)! 📍16595 Redmond Way

latestPosts.caption: Pomegranate Bistro is turning 20! 🎉 🎉 Celebrate all summer long with throwback menu specials, fun surprises, and community cheer. Don’t miss cookbook signings, $10 deals, and a kids’ menu design contest! 🍽️🥂 @pombistro

latestPosts.caption: Stay cool and sip on sunshine! ☀️🍓 Beat the heat with refreshing cold-pressed juices and smoothies at @nekterredmond in Redmond. Perfectly fresh, naturally delicious, and just what you need to keep energized all summer long!

Huge thanks to everyone who joined us at the Soccer Watch Party at Redmond Town Center! ⚽💚 The sun was out, the crowd was loud, and the Sounders spirit was strong. We loved celebrating with you—until next time! 🙌🌞

The annual VegFest is happening this weekend at Downtown Park in Redmond! 🎉🌱 

All are welcome for a day of plant-powered eats, free samples, live music, Zumba, yoga, adorable animals, and fun like cookie decorating and spice blending. 🍪🧘‍♀️🌶️🐐 It’s a family-friendly fest full of flavor and fun—don’t miss it! 💚
